...\n第 20 次對話：傳 幾萬 tokens\n"}]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"呢個係 LLM 嘅基本運作方式——AI 需要看到完整對話歷史先能理解 context。但問題係，好多人開咗一個 session 就用成日，越用越貴。"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"我自己嘅情況："}]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["TUI 底部會實時顯示 token 用量，例如 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"tokens 10k/272k (4%)"}],"。跑住 5 個 Agent（main、crawler、webtest、coder、social），如果唔留意，一個長 session 可以輕易消耗幾萬 token。"]}],"\n",["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4 flex gap-3 rounded-xl border-l-4 p-4 shadow-sm bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-300","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 shrink-0","children":["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-triangle-alert h-5 w-5 text-yellow-600","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","wmoenq",{"d":"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3"}],["$","path","juzpu7",{"d":"M12 9v4"}],["$","path","p32p05",{"d":"M12 17h.01"}],"$undefined"]}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-sm","children":["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"最危險嘅組合："}]," 長 session + 頂級模型（Claude Opus 4.6 / GPT-5.4）。一個跑咗幾小時嘅 Coder Agent session，token 消耗可以係新 session 嘅 10–50 倍。"]}]}]]}],"\n",["$","hr",null,{}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-12 mb-4 border-l-4 border-red-600 pl-4 text-2xl font-bold","id":"招一定期開新-session","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#招一定期開新-session","children":"招一：定期開新 Session"}]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"最簡單、效果最大嘅一招。"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"為什麼有效："}]," 新 session 冇歷史 context，每次對話只傳你當前嘅指令，token 消耗係最低點。"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"3 種開新 Session 嘅方法："}]}],"\n",["$","figure",null,{"data-rehype-pretty-code-figure":"","chil