4d:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：OpenClaw 本身使唔使錢？"}]}]
4e:["$","p",null,{"children":["OpenClaw 軟件本身係開源免費。費用嚟自你用嘅 LLM API——即係每次 OpenClaw 問 Claude 或 GPT 問題時嘅 API call 費用。軟件免費，但跑 AI 嘅算力要錢。詳細睇",["$","a",null,{"href":"/compare/vs-chatgpt","children":"OpenClaw vs ChatGPT 費用比較"}],"。"]}]
4f:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：用本地模型係咪完全免費？"}]}]
50:["$","p",null,{"children":"係，本地模型（例如透過 Ollama 跑 Llama、Mistral 等）唔需要 API 費用。但你需要有足夠嘅硬件：Apple Silicon Mac（M1/M2/M3/M4）或者有獨立 GPU 嘅 PC。模型質素亦通常低過頂級雲端模型。適合想完全本地化、唔想有任何費用嘅用戶。"}]
51:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：點知我而家燒咗幾多錢？"}]}]
52:["$","p",null,{"children":["兩個地方睇：一係 TUI 底部嘅實時 token 顯示（",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"tokens X/Y (Z%)"}],"），可以估算當前 session 嘅消耗。二係你嘅 API provider dashboard——OpenAI 有 Usage 頁面、Anthropic 有 Console 用量統計，都可以睇到實際費用。建議每隔幾日睇一次直至習慣咗自己嘅用量模式。"]}]
53:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：有冇方法設用量上限，用完就停？"}]}]
54:["$","p",null,{"children":["有。OpenAI 同 Anthropic 都支持喺 dashboard 設 hard limit，達到上限後 API call 會返回錯誤，OpenClaw 就唔能再發出請求。另外 OpenClaw config 入面都可以設 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"budget.daily_limit"}],"，達到後會根據你設嘅 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"on_limit"}]," 行為（warn / stop / fallback to cheaper model）處理。強烈建議兩個都設。"]}]
